Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:18.88,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(485,320)}{\fad(500,0)}然後、第一次的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是加奈啊 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早睡早起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有兩圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來加奈最近經常遲到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 放學的時候也是 一下課馬上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？交到男朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就是…就是 別亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上這樣說 其實已經約好去遊樂園約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游…遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不可以哦 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那種不純潔而且淫猥的地方 絕對不能去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？美華醬 妳討厭遊樂園嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想下次邀請美華醬 大家一起去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大概辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑得越來越好了呢 中町同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起春季時 越來越快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來有好好做過基礎鍛煉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈每天早上都在跑步 很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦 不光是我 美華醬也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 美華醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 那個…加奈邀請的話去遊樂園也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊樂園是約會的最佳地點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是她男朋友在等她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男…妳說男朋友會伏擊她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是等她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fs22}まちぶせ（伏擊）和まちあわせ（等）音差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 比如搭男朋友的自行車每天上下學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不可以 自行車乘兩人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被交警逮捕判死刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是騎不好 怎樣才能騎好自行車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美…美華醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美華醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 這個是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的 這種日子我也有過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別隨便就認同了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我不會跟誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會永遠藏在心裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾取出來欣賞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}{\an7}字：偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 會仔細品味的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦 加奈 美華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 騎自行車的練習？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 騎著那個練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 加奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今往後每天由我騎自行車接送加奈去學校也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？美華醬不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行車乘兩人的話會被交警罵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這種事我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰想和加奈乘自行車啊…自行車…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次兩人各騎一輛去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 還有這招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 美華醬 妳會騎自行車了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 沒問題了 做什麼事情都是如魚得水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎~好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 加奈的話 比我差的遠咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我在心中也是駕輕就熟的自行車好手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那樣的話就比比誰能騎好自行車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是比賽是吧 我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是要怎樣比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還用問嗎 對我們來說不是有那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？加奈妳想逃避嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 因為那個是小孩子玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得騎那個好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼想騎的話 美華醬一個人去騎也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,減薪啊 減薪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先這樣模擬騎著自行車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開始決勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時恭候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路段是學校後門到這個公園這段 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要上了哦 準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 那是在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 前方是交叉路口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能輸等妳 衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快馬加鞭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 美華醬 扣1分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為交叉路口要慢下來看左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那繼續了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 突然有輛卡車停在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美…美華醬 我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一點 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷得並不重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最…最後見到那個人 見到約翰尼後幫我告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fs22}約翰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我是個不成熟的女人 對不起"  幫我傳…達…給…他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已經這個時候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美華醬 我要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混…混蛋約翰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 不知不覺中 今天我和美華醬在公園模擬練習騎自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經用完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天得去買一本新的日記本了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的V
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經10點了 得快點睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,種類真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個價格是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2…2980日元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說裡面附帶藏寶圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 有誰在裡面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人在裡面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只能放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢姐 補習班放學了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要買嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的事 這種奢侈品 我不會買的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼難得的 我給妳買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是很想要嗎？這本日記本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說很想要 但沒有理由就給我買 我覺得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是想包養年輕可愛的孩子的大叔心境如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些夠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fs22}字：哦呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要像小遙姐那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈那傢伙 那傢伙一定是那個叫約翰尼的款爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yahoo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還是想要那個日記本啊 那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2980日元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 吶 加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 明天放學回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以順便幫我買兩個日記本麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 兩本是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦 給妳錢 找回的零錢就給加奈醬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的 小夢姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢是農家的伯伯一粒一粒飽含苦心種的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是米麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就是說必須好好要珍惜錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 差不多要洗晚飯的大米了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 小夢 兩本日記本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與妳緊緊相連的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就做好的令人愉快的晚飯咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我就會毫不客氣地全部收下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬和日向不一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 換成代理肯定也是一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的 不是有諺語也這麼說麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的就是我的 我的還是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有那種諺語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說要避免一切口實 做點讓她強行收下的小手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想這樣做也許能成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 能把妳那邊的醬油遞給我下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 請用代理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬 稍微麻煩妳一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳那邊的廣告單請給我50份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 妳知道我的路線手冊放哪了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路線手冊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在那裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬 可以幫我嘗下蛋糕的味道麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 過來一下可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬 罵我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴 妳這●●●●
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳讓我說什麼呢 小遙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也相當不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 妳在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊 加奈 喬尼的同伴麥克呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為某貓的不良事故 被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋約翰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都辛苦啦 我要發這個月份的工資了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 代理 薪水袋我這多了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個月讓妳做了很多雜事 這是臨時的獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個40個1日元的硬幣和4個10日元的硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有100日元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 全部加起來2980日元
